#PLOT AND ACF

#Trend predictor has a very small p-value meaning so it is a good predictor.Seasonality can be observed from the residuals (de-trended UGS). #De-trended acf #Ljung-Box test has low p value. #Significant autocorrelation at 2,4,6,8

#TREN+SEASONALITY

#ADD LAG 2

dt[,UGS_lag2:=c(rep(NA,2),dt$UGS[1:(28)], rep(NA,4-2))]
